code: @Override public Set<SimpSession> getSessions() {     return new HashSet<>(this.sessions.values()). }
@Override public SimpSession getSession(String sessionId) {     return this.sessions.get(sessionId). }
public void addSessions(TestSimpSession... sessions) {     for (TestSimpSession session : sessions) {         session.setUser(this).         this.sessions.put(session.getId(), session).     } }
@Override public boolean equals(Object other) {     return (this == other || (other instanceof SimpUser && this.name.equals(((SimpUser) other).getName()))). }
@Override public String toString() {     return "name=" + this.name + ", sessions=" + this.sessions. }
